  "texts": [
    "In the \"two-person manual annotation\" strategy, two annotators finished a set of 22 full articles individually and then compared their results.",
    "The inter-annotator agreement was 98.3%.",
    "In the \"three-person manual annotation\" strategy, three annotators annotated another set of 14 full articles, reaching 93.1% agreement.The overall annotating process is still time consuming.",
    "On average, it took an annotator 40-45 min to finish one article and 20-25 min to review one article.",
    "In practice, the three-person manual annotation and the two-person annotation strategies were implemented on 200 articles, respectively."
  ],
